    <url>/2023/10/02/PCFixing-WhiteScreen-Bug/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="故障演示"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#故障演示"></a> 故障演示</h1>
<iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=449210841&bvid=BV1jj411b7dz&cid=1286850679&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true" style="width: 100%; height: 500px; max-width: 100%；align:center; padding:20px 0;"> </iframe>
<h1 id="故障原因"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#故障原因"></a> 故障原因</h1>
<p>一句话概括：KB5022913补丁和startallback插件有冲突引起的</p>
<p>参考链接：</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.chiphell.com/thread-2500922-1-1.html">https://www.chiphell.com/thread-2500922-1-1.html</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.chiphell.com/thread-2500697-1-1.html">https://www.chiphell.com/thread-2500697-1-1.html</a></li>
</ul>
<h1 id="解决方案"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#解决方案"></a> 解决方案</h1>
<p>强制重启三次电脑，自动进入安全模式后，卸载KB5022913补丁或startallback插件即可</p>
<p>也可进入PE进行卸载。</p>
]]></content>
